author: Aldous Huxley
message: Experience is not what happens to a man. It is what a man does with what happens to him.
title: Thought of the day

message: A good teacher is like a candle it consumes itself to light the way for others.
title: Thought of the day

author: Oscar Wilde
message: The only thing to do with good advice is to pass it on. It is never of any use to oneself.
title: Thought of the day

message: Life is not measured by the breaths we take, but by the moments that take our breath.
